{"id": "ChIJs9ffPWOAhYARmAMw6_TbdNo", "rating": 4.1, "userRatingCount": 125, "displayName": {"text": "Whole Cakes - SoMa", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Petite bakery featuring organic & gluten-free goodies, including custom cakes, cookies & muffins.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJs9ffPWOAhYARmAMw6_TbdNo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xGTmRWUTFTRTFrWDNwSll6azRZMGRWT0ZGU04zYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "I really love the coffee cake the cappuccino was very tasty but the person working seemed nervous pressured and in a rush even though I was the first person there.  There was suddenly a line behind me but they did not seem time restrained.  Maybe he should hire workers since he may have been the owner.  It’s like 200 sq ft super small be prepared to take everything to go!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I really love the coffee cake the cappuccino was very tasty but the person working seemed nervous pressured and in a rush even though I was the first person there.  There was suddenly a line behind me but they did not seem time restrained.  Maybe he should hire workers since he may have been the owner.  It’s like 200 sq ft super small be prepared to take everything to go!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Yasmin Paculba", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103483223888665595690/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLqRxx7ur1Vfl0JB81VHmKcINLxh1yi0zYBB1tMpPMIL5QAaw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-07T17:52:51.026863047Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xGTmRWUTFTRTFrWDNwSll6azRZMGRWT0ZGU04zYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xGTmRWUTFTRTFrWDNwSll6azRZMGRWT0ZGU04zYxAB!2m1!1s0x808580633ddfd7b3:0xda74dbf4eb300398"}, {"name": "places/ChIJs9ffPWOAhYARmAMw6_TbdNo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT205MVl6WnNOR0pQZUZodmMzUlFRVEpUUjJVMVFtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 2, "text": {"text": "Never been here before. Passed by and got intrigued by the Asian flavors on the sign. They all look lovely, so I picked four different slices to try it out. However, I’m really disappointed with the results. Three of them taste sugarless and have a stale taste from refrigeration, which is usually a sign of being not fresh. Yet, the classic hojicha tastes too sweet. Each slice costs around $11, not worth it.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Never been here before. Passed by and got intrigued by the Asian flavors on the sign. They all look lovely, so I picked four different slices to try it out. However, I’m really disappointed with the results. Three of them taste sugarless and have a stale taste from refrigeration, which is usually a sign of being not fresh. Yet, the classic hojicha tastes too sweet. Each slice costs around $11, not worth it.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Adam Chung", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104358251372416271450/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXdhr794kMCbPdqqMSzHLc6yMGcdTp3KmHfAKETzzPbYgohHWGa=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-15T02:04:09.443767247Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT205MVl6WnNOR0pQZUZodmMzUlFRVEpUUjJVMVFtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT205MVl6WnNOR0pQZUZodmMzUlFRVEpUUjJVMVFtYxAB!2m1!1s0x808580633ddfd7b3:0xda74dbf4eb300398"}, {"name": "places/ChIJs9ffPWOAhYARmAMw6_TbdNo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21NeFoyZ3hkVUZpUTBneGMwdHRiM1puUzFZMU9HYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "They moved but the cake is equally great!\nLove the cookies, coffee, and most impressive the pistachio cake - sooo good.\nHighly recommend.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "They moved but the cake is equally great!\nLove the cookies, coffee, and most impressive the pistachio cake - sooo good.\nHighly recommend.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Yusi", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116680446531147874736/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8uoy0fZPJTsUuL3h0ZIpihJvRC7ufazApZKXlOiywJ2YxZ2QG=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-09T16:29:29.976238089Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21NeFoyZ3hkVUZpUTBneGMwdHRiM1puUzFZMU9HYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21NeFoyZ3hkVUZpUTBneGMwdHRiM1puUzFZMU9HYxAB!2m1!1s0x808580633ddfd7b3:0xda74dbf4eb300398"}, {"name": "places/ChIJs9ffPWOAhYARmAMw6_TbdNo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25GblZrMUlNWEpSUTE5d1FWTkNZVzB6Vkc1TmJIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The cakes are great, not overly sweet and are clearly made with clean ingredients. The salt breads are INCREDIBLE! My apartment is nearby and I can't get enough of them with my morning coffee.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The cakes are great, not overly sweet and are clearly made with clean ingredients. The salt breads are INCREDIBLE! My apartment is nearby and I can't get enough of them with my morning coffee.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Rachel Wise", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100398145979142545220/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU-x8VEBvKhLIeRdOI_C4qIz0FJW1Zx_Pko0BNlt1GZsGF1w71cNg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-01T14:46:18.505428067Z", "flagConte